title: Wireless Bluetooth Headphones
description: Experience crystal-clear sound with our premium wireless headphones. Featuring active noise cancellation, 30-hour battery life, and ultra-comfortable ear cushions. Perfect for travel, work, or relaxing at home. Includes carrying case and 3.5mm audio cable for wired listening.

title: Smart Fitness Watch
description: Track every aspect of your health with this advanced smartwatch. Monitors heart rate, blood oxygen, sleep patterns, and stress levels. Waterproof design with 7-day battery life. Includes GPS tracking for runs and 20+ workout modes. Syncs with both Android and iOS devices.

title: Organic Cotton T-Shirt
description: 100% certified organic cotton t-shirt with a perfect relaxed fit. Breathable fabric keeps you cool all day. Available in 12 colors. Machine washable with minimal shrinkage. Ethically produced in fair trade facilities.

title: Stainless Steel Water Bottle
description: Premium insulated water bottle keeps drinks cold for 24 hours or hot for 12 hours. Leak-proof design with one-handed operation. 32oz capacity with wide mouth for easy filling. BPA-free and dishwasher safe.

title: Wireless Phone Charger
description: Fast-charging Qi-certified wireless charger with anti-slip silicone surface. Charges through most phone cases up to 5mm thick. Includes built-in temperature control and foreign object detection for safety.

title: Leather Wallet
description: Handcrafted genuine leather bifold wallet with RFID blocking technology. 8 card slots, 2 ID windows, and full-length bill compartment. Ages beautifully over time with natural patina.

title: Yoga Mat
description: Extra thick 1/2 inch yoga mat provides superior cushioning for joints. Non-slip textured surface ensures stability in all poses. Includes carrying strap and is free from harmful phthalates and latex.
